---
title: Mexican-Spiced Shrimp Bowls with Jewelled Rice and Red Sauce
description: Is there anything better than digging into a bountiful rice bowl? Packed with smoky aromatic spices, crisp veggies and red sauce-slathered shrimp, this festive dish will immediately transport you to Mexico (no passport required!).
